{
  "stem": "1677.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 330.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I-- we had different rules where I come from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you haven't shown me-- it's your fault.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You should have told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's your fault.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he swallowed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He realized that he made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he fixed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He showed me how to fix it-- if I break a thread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I did break many threads, because I didn't think it was important.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I thought it was such a joke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were weaving parachute linen for the German Luftwaffe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In March, in April, in May, 1945, I, when the world was in pieces, I was standing, weaving for the German Luftwaffe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And one day, in the-- the routine in the camp, in that surface-- always very simple.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] in the morning-- get up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We jumped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had beautiful showers there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We showered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We put on our clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We didn't have lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were-- it was hygienic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had to clean every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I never did, but others did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then-- then we got our coffee for breakfast, I think, or whatever-- or soup, maybe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then we went-- but then they counted us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They counted us three times a day in the freezing-- it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So my feet were all swollen from the cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then came Christmas, 1944-- Christmas Eve.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You must understand that there were girls with me, women, a bit older than me, who never knew they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because they were German, and they suddenly discovered that one Aryan-- non-Aryan grandmother, when they had to prove their Aryan descendancy, [NON-ENGLISH], and they couldn't prove their Aryan [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they were sent to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And in the end too, there was a girl, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
